'''百魔洞'''是中国的一处旅游景点。位于[[广西省|广西省]][[巴马县|巴马县]]城西北部的坡月村，是一个天然的[[石灰岩|石灰岩]][[溶洞|溶洞]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.xinhuanet.com/science/2018-07/14/c_137321847.htm |title = 神奇的巴马百魔洞 |accessdate = 2021-03-13 |dead-url = no |archive-date = 2018-07-19 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180719144911/http://www.xinhuanet.com/science/2018-07/14/c_137321847.htm }}</ref>。该溶洞的平均高度80米，宽70米。洞内最高[[石笋|石笋]]为39米、直径10米。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://travel.sina.com.cn/china/p/2008-11-18/110237251.shtml |title = 非凡的体验——广西巴马百魔洞 |accessdate = 2021-03-15 |dead-url = no |archive-date = 2020-09-18 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200918115324/http://travel.sina.com.cn/china/p/2008-11-18/110237251.shtml }}</ref>。

